@*
    Root document component for the Blazor Web App per AD-0004.

    Replaces the legacy _Host.cshtml + standalone Blazor Server
    bootstrap. Mapped via app.MapRazorComponents<App>() in
    Program.cs; the framework renders this component as the HTML
    document at the root of every Razor-Components-served route.

    The default render mode for components hosted under this
    document is Static SSR (per AD-0004's matrix). Components that
    need interactivity opt in with `@rendermode InteractiveServer`
    at the top of their .razor file (TD-0016 step 1). The server
    must call `.AddInteractiveServerRenderMode()` on the
    `MapRazorComponents<App>()` builder for those opt-ins to take
    effect.
*@
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <base href="/" />
    <HeadOutlet />
    <title>TabFlow Platform</title>
</head>
<body>
    <Routes />
    <script src="_framework/blazor.web.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
